\id 3JN - Fulfulde Benin 
\h Yuhaana Tata…ďol 
\toc1 ∆äerewol Yuhaana Tata…ďol 
\toc2 Yuhaana Tata…ďol 
\mt1 ∆äerewol Yuhaana Tata…ďol  
\is1 Haala pu…ó…óirka  
\ip Gorko bi'etee…óo Gayus nun Yuhaana winnani …óerewol mum Ňčol …óo  
\im EŇčol batana bo kade him…ďe …ói…óo wo…ď…ďe: Diyoterefes e Demeteriyus. EŇčol tii…óina wallugo him…ďe woositintoo…ďe e fiina linjiila. Gayus wallitii iri ma…ď…ďe de …óuu…ó…óum, Yuhaana bo yettii mo no woo…ói gam oo ja…ď…ďoo ho…ď…ďe, amma Diyoterefes kan salake wallugo …ďe.  
\im Yuhaana manii Demeteriyus gam geeta ka him…ďe batanta mo.  
\iot Tokkontirki haalaaji  
\io1 1. Haala pu…ó…óirka, 1-3  
\io1 2. Manoore Gayus, 4-8  
\io1 3. Gaccaago Diyoterefes, 9-10  
\io1 4. Demeteriyus yerdaama, 11-12  
\io1 5. Cannooje, 13-15.  
\c 1  
\s1 Sannoore  
\p
\v 1 Min dottiijo\x + \xo 1.1 \xt 2 Yuhaana. 1.\x*, winni …óerewol Ňčol. Mii winnanee an banniraawo am Gayus, ji…óaa…óo der gooŇča.   
\p
\v 2 Banniraawo am ji…óaa…óo, mii eela huune fu yahanee yeeso, …ďannu maa yan…óa hande no yonki maa yan…óiri.  
\v 3 ∆Āerne am weli sanne no banniraa…ďe wo…ď…ďe wari seedanii am no tinnori…óaa der gooŇča, e no jahirtaa der gooŇča bo.  
\v 4 Walaa ko …ďuri welingo …ďerne am, to hinaa nanugo no …ďikkol am e yaha der gooŇča.   
\s1 Manoore Gayus  
\p
\v 5 Banniraawo am ji…óaa…óo, golle geete …óe ga…óataa e wallugo banniraa…ďe baa to …ďee ho…ď…ďe e hollita aa koolinii…óo\f + \fr 1.5 \ft Banniraa…ďe …ďen laatii sankitoo…ďe linjiila.\f*.  
\v 6 ∆Āe ceedake yidde maa yeeso jama'aare goon…óin…ďe …óo. Wallu …ďe hande no fottiranta Alla der jahaaŇčal ma…ď…ďe, den a wa…óii ko woo…ói.  
\v 7 Gam inne Almasiihu …ďe ga…ói jahaaŇčal ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ke…ďay go…ó…óum e juu…óe …ďe goon…óinay.  
\v 8 Gam majjum haani, balliten him…ďe iri ma…ď…ďe, gam golliden e ma…ď…ďe der fiinugo gooŇča.   
\s1 Feloore Diyoterefes  
\p
\v 9 Mi winnanii jama'aare goon…óin…ďe …óerewol, amma Diyoterefes, ji…ó…óo ardingo hoore mum ja…ďay haala amen.  
\v 10 Gam majjum, to mi warii, mi hollan ko o wa…óata e no o biisirta inne amen. Kanjum tan bane: O ja…ď…ďataako banniraa…ďe ho…ď…ďe, kade bo, yi…óu…ďe ja…ď…ďaago …ďe, oo ha…óa …óum, oo riiwa …ďe diga e eklesiya.   
\s1 Manoore Demeteriyus  
\p
\v 11 Banniraawo am ji…óaa…óo, taa yemmin ko boni, yemmin ko woo…ói. Ga…óoowo ko woo…ói fu, ne…ó…óo Alla nun. Ga…óoowo ko halli bo, annaa Alla.   
\p
\v 12 Demeteriyus kan, him…ďe fu e seedanoo …óum ko woo…ói, gooŇča e hoore mum bo e seedanoo mo …óum. Menen bo, emen ceedo …óum, aa anni bo seedaaku amen e laatii gooŇča.   
\s1 Cannooje  
\p
\v 13 Ko haani mi winnanee e …óuu…ói, amma mi yi…óaa winnugo …óum …óum fu der …óerewol e dawa.  
\v 14 Mii haa…ďi yi'ugo maa law, gam badden hunnuko e hunnuko.   
\p
\v 15 Igoo…ďe maa won…ďe …óo fu sannii maa. Mi sannii banniraa…ďe fu, gooto gooto. Jam wona e maa.   